# mojo-type-and-api-migration — History

## v1.0.0 (2026-05-18) — Merge of 40 skills (M3 sub-PR 2/4)

**Changed by:** Skill-merge swarm (Phase D, M3 type-api-migration sub-cluster / #1772)
**Verification:** verified-local

### What changed

Consolidated 40 Mojo type/API migration skills as the second of 4
sequential M3 (Mojo mega-cluster) sub-PRs. Covers: stdlib import
qualification, parametric dtype migration, trait conformance (Boolable,
Writable, ImplicitlyCopyable, Module), API name reconciliation, overload
disambiguation, `escaping` keyword removal, circular import resolution,
Python interop → stdlib migration, FP16 SIMD upgrade, sequential parametric
containers, set() API migration patterns, and version migration strategy.

---

